    "en": {
      "title": "CCD goes to parliament",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that a team of officials from the Colombo Crimes Division has arrived in Parliament yesterday (23rd) to obtain statements from the Members of Parliament regarding the incidents of rioters damaging the properties including the houses of the Members of Parliament.",
        "Statements have been obtained from several Members of Parliament and statements will be obtained from other Members of Parliament in the future.",
        "Riots on May 9 damaged property, including the homes of about 75 members of parliament."
      ],
